Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.10,0:01:32.53,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,One hundred ten years ago…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.53,0:01:34.23,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,As a result of high turnover
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.23,0:01:36.67,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,among the captains of\Nthe Thirteen Court Guard Squads,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.67,0:01:39.80,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,a new generation was\Nabout to take over.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.47,0:01:42.53,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,As part of the changeover,\NKisuke Urahara,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.53,0:01:45.86,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,filled the empty post of\NSquad 12 captain
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.86,0:01:48.32,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,at the recommendation of\NYoruichi Shihoin,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.32,0:01:51.62,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,who at the time,\Nwas captain of Squad 2.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.22,0:01:56.03,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,However, Hiyori Sarugaki,\Nlieutenant of Squad 12,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.03,0:01:58.95,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,had a strained relationship\Nwith Urahara,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.95,0:02:02.67,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,due to the dislike of\Nhis history
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.67,0:02:05.54,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,in the Stealth Force and\Nhis laid-back personality.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.50,0:02:10.74,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What the hell is all of this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.22,0:02:16.18,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Just where do you \Nthink this is, you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.18,0:02:17.56,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the captain's room!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.56,0:02:19.03,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,The captain's room!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.03,0:02:22.65,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't just go and\Ndo your own renovations!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.65,0:02:24.30,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.61,0:02:26.63,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, it's my room.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.63,0:02:27.63,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.81,0:02:31.56,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, it's not a renovation.\NI just did a little rearranging.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.56,0:02:33.10,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,How is this "rearranging"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.46,0:02:37.39,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,There's absolutely nothing\Nof the old room left!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.03,0:02:46.51,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yes…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.95,0:02:50.96,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a favor to\Nask of you, Hiyori.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.22,0:02:52.72,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.67,0:02:57.05,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to come with me\Nright now to the Maggot's Nest.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.87,0:03:01.33,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Maggot's Nest?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.28,0:03:26.43,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, we're here.\NThis is the place.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.66,0:03:27.64,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.38,0:03:32.79,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Kisuke's here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.79,0:03:37.23,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! He said he already had\Nyour permission, Lady Yoruichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.68,0:03:42.70,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What was it now?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.05,0:03:44.54,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.09,0:03:48.45,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,If you do not recall,\Nshall I have him leave?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.45,0:03:50.04,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,No, that won't be necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.36,0:03:52.43,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Take him wherever\Nhe wants to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.86,0:03:54.55,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.42,0:03:57.52,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.78,0:03:59.27,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Lady Yoruichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.27,0:04:01.99,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What now Soi Fon?\NDon't be so noisy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.53,0:04:04.48,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,But…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.48,0:04:05.99,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,No need to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.43,0:04:09.75,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Knowing Kisuke,\Nhe came here for a reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.74,0:04:16.00,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh… It opened, it opened.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.00,0:04:17.35,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Shall we go in?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.35,0:04:18.53,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.53,0:04:20.57,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now, don't be like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.57,0:04:22.30,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.23,0:04:25.30,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.30,0:04:27.23,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I said I don't want to!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.59,0:04:29.18,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,– Now, now…\N– Let go of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.18,0:04:31.22,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,When you go in, who knows,\Nyou might think,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.22,0:04:33.95,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,– "Wow, it's wonderful!"\N– I said let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.12,0:04:39.16,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought we were going\Nto some creepy place
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.16,0:04:41.24,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,called the "Maggot's Nest."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.24,0:04:43.19,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,We're inside\Nthe Squad 2 Barrack grounds!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.63,0:04:46.93,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You've heard of the Stealth Force,\Nhaven't you, Hiyori?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.93,0:04:48.51,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Stealth Force?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.51,0:04:51.43,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Well of course I have.\NIt's your old unit, idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.43,0:04:52.97,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop changing the subject!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.39,0:05:02.26,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,STEALTH FORCE
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.95,0:04:56.41,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Stealth Force.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.86,0:04:59.30,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It is an organization whose\Norigins are separate
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.30,0:05:01.59,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,from the Thirteen Court\NGuard Squads.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.90,0:05:06.42,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,As one of the four\Ngreat noble clans
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.42,0:05:08.18,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,who possess incredible\NSoul Reaper powers,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.18,0:05:09.75,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,the Shihoin Clan serves as
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.75,0:05:11.74,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,the supreme commander\Nto this force.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.36,0:05:14.76,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,And whenever the head\Nof the Shihoin Clan
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.76,0:05:16.88,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,becomes a captain of\Na Thirteen Court Guard Squad,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.88,0:05:18.72,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,the squad they lead\Nhas a tendency to
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.72,0:05:21.30,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,become closely associated\Nwith the Stealth Force.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.77,0:05:23.76,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,So that means, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.49,0:05:28.13,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yoruichi,\Nthe current supreme commander,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.13,0:05:30.52,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,concurrently serves as\Ncaptain of Squad 2.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.22,0:05:34.86,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That means the current Stealth Force\Nbecomes much like an organization
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.86,0:05:37.82,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,under the direct control\Nof Squad 2.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.94,0:05:42.10,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,The Stealth Force is\Ndivided into five units,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.10,0:05:44.32,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,and each unit leader is also\Na Seat Officer of Squad 2.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.89,0:05:49.84,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I was the leader of Unit Three,\N"Confinement Troops."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.88,0:05:53.20,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Then you were a yard hack?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.86,0:05:56.90,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,No…I was a prison guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.97,0:06:00.60,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,My main duties were to imprison
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.60,0:06:03.88,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,and watch over those who\Ncommitted crimes inside the Seireitei.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.88,0:06:05.53,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,So that made you\Na yard hack, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.53,0:06:06.91,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I was a guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.11,0:06:08.26,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Same thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.26,0:06:11.79,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Your job was to swagger about\Nin front of the criminals, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.84,0:06:19.32,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,The Confinement Troops\Nhad another duty
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.86,0:06:22.86,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,as Special Confinement officers.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.86,0:06:25.59,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Special Confinement officer?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.04,0:06:27.15,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Our job was to
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.15,0:06:31.05,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,investigate, apprehend and\Nkeep under surveillance
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.05,0:06:33.42,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Soul Reapers joining\Nthe Court Guard Squads
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.42,0:06:36.04,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,whose ideas and\Nactions would
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.04,0:06:38.58,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,either put other\NSoul Reapers at risk,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.58,0:06:41.58,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,or posed a threat by\Nobstructing the squad's duties.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.74,0:06:43.08,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't understand what you said!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.05,0:06:45.97,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You have a confusing\Nway of saying things!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.97,0:06:48.01,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Say it in simple terms.\NSimple terms!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.01,0:06:52.17,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, my job was to catch\Nand lock up dangerous elements
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.17,0:06:55.03,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,within the Thirteen Court\NGuard Squads.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.79,0:06:59.63,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That facility is located here,\Nin Squad 2's barracks.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.20,0:07:04.27,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,The facility is on the northwest\Nside of these grounds,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.27,0:07:06.13,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,beyond the huge\N54-meter-wide moat.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.11,0:07:16.68,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,The Underground Special\NConfinement Station.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.16,0:07:21.17,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Also known as \Nthe Maggot's Nest.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.73,0:07:44.40,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.40,0:07:46.70,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,The inside is nothing\Nbut a huge cave.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.40,0:07:50.75,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you really keep\Npeople locked up in here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.75,0:07:52.14,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,In this underground prison?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.14,0:07:54.49,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It does sound cruel, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.39,0:07:58.49,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,But it isn't really\Nan underground prison.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.20,0:08:06.86,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.31,0:08:19.54,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,They are not allowed\Nto leave this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.54,0:08:22.56,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,However, their activities within\Nthe facility are not restricted.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.85,0:08:34.30,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Please be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.80,0:08:38.33,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Sometimes someone\Nwill attack all of a sudden.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.88,0:08:44.16,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What on earth did these people do?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.52,0:08:45.56,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.65,0:08:48.22,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,As I told you…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.22,0:08:50.77,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,These people haven't\Ndone anything wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.69,0:08:55.93,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,They are people who\Nwere determined to be
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.93,0:08:58.95,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,"dangerous elements" according\Nto the criteria of the Seireitei.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.63,0:09:02.84,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,They've committed no crime,\Nso we cannot try them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.21,0:09:06.66,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,However, left free,\Nthey may be dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.66,0:09:08.96,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That is why we keep them\Nconfined in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.70,0:09:11.93,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that about?!\NI don't get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.93,0:09:13.42,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,They haven't done anything,\Nand yet you…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.42,0:09:14.43,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Hiyori…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.83,0:09:17.45,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Up until now, have there\Nbeen any among your peers
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.45,0:09:19.14,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,who resigned from\Nthe Thirteen Court Guard Squads?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.14,0:09:20.00,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.42,0:09:22.61,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,There's been a couple, but…\Nwhat about them?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.20,0:09:27.61,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,The truth is, there is no system\Nthat allows members to "resign."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.51,0:09:32.56,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Those who have no choice\Nbut to leave the squad
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.56,0:09:34.72,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,for personal reasons are\Non Squad Leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.72,0:09:36.27,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,If it does not seem likely that
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.27,0:09:37.93,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,they will be able to\Nreturn to the squad
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.93,0:09:39.66,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,for an extended period of time,\Nit is considered an "Expulsion."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.62,0:09:44.25,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,We do not recognize leaving\Nthe squad by one's own choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.25,0:09:45.34,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.64,0:09:48.83,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,"Resigning" means they are\Nplaced under "special confinement."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.29,0:09:52.10,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Squad members who\Nare reported to have resigned
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.10,0:09:54.17,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,are all sent here for confinement.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.10,0:09:58.32,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Why go through all that trouble?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.86,0:10:01.58,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,The Thirteen Court Guard Squads\Nis a noble organization.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.13,0:10:04.49,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It must never produce\Nany unsuitable members
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.49,0:10:06.62,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,from among those who were once\Naccepted into the organization.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.20,0:10:11.33,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That is the philosophy of\NCentral 46 that rules the Seireitei.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.16,0:10:14.81,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That is why "unsuitables" who might\Nbecome "dangerous elements"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.81,0:10:17.55,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,are dealt with in utmost secrecy\Nas deserters.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.70,0:10:20.56,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Hiyori…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.03,0:10:23.55,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Something has\Nbeen on my mind
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.55,0:10:25.42,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,ever since I was assigned\Nhere as unit leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.57,0:10:30.17,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, the people here\Nare all dangerous people.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.50,0:10:32.62,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,But I was thinking there\Nare many people here
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.62,0:10:34.44,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,whose risk could be\Nturned to a huge good
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.44,0:10:36.56,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,if we could only\Nprovide them an environment
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.56,0:10:39.55,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,where they could put\Ntheir abilities to use.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.96,0:10:41.38,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Which is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.38,0:10:43.69,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You're keeping them confined because\Nthey're dangerous elements, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.69,0:10:46.18,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,But now, you're talking about\Nputting their ability to use.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.18,0:10:47.01,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Hiyori?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.38,0:10:50.86,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that you, Hiyori?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.86,0:10:52.33,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Mouth?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.58,0:10:56.35,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,He's one of my peers\Nwhom I thought had deserted.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.35,0:10:59.73,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,He always used to talk big and boast\Nabout things he couldn't even do,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.73,0:11:01.79,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,like one day being\Nin charge of the Seireitei,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.79,0:11:03.18,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,so everyone called him\N"Big Mouth."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.18,0:11:05.43,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Hiyori!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.43,0:11:06.43,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Hiyori!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.43,0:11:08.28,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Help me!\NYou've got to help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.97,0:11:11.72,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,We were classmates, right?\NI want to go home!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.72,0:11:13.30,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to go home, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.70,0:11:24.33,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Shoot! I left my sword\Nin the barracks.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.49,0:11:37.68,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.56,0:11:41.65,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew you forgot your sword,\Nbut I kept quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.70,0:11:46.83,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Bringing weapons into the Special\NConfinement Station is forbidden.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.50,0:11:51.66,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why it is an absolute\N requirement that leaders of
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.66,0:11:56.46,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,the Confinement Troops be able\N to subdue everyone unarmed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.03,0:12:02.26,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,How sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.76,0:12:06.00,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you forgotten my face\Nafter just two or three days?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.93,0:12:09.53,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,After I took such\Ngood care of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.30,0:12:23.29,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.73,0:12:24.72,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Get them!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.06,0:12:44.17,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Seems you all\Nhave really forgotten me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.17,0:12:46.11,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,How cruel.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.53,0:12:55.88,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.98,0:13:01.96,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen! I want you to get me\Nout of here right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.96,0:13:03.84,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't, I'll…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.37,0:13:08.90,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.36,0:13:13.10,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You've taken the wrong person\Nas a hostage.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.23,0:13:21.91,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't mess with me, idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.59,0:13:26.11,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,His big mouth\Njust got a lot bigger.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.62,0:13:27.66,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Good grief…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.30,0:13:30.59,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Shall we go, Hiyori?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.80,0:13:36.39,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What sort of environment\Nare you talking about
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.39,0:13:37.74,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,that'll make\Nthese guys useful?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.74,0:13:39.87,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,They're really dangerous elements!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.87,0:13:43.44,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,If you bring these guys outside,\Nyou'll just increase your problems!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.40,0:13:47.77,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now…\NIn any case, let's get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.06,0:14:04.06,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Take a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.90,0:14:07.26,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Beyond here is the only\Ndangerous element
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.26,0:14:09.89,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,in this place in\Nsolitary confinement.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.93,0:14:13.36,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You mean someone\Neven more violent?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.90,0:14:16.54,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What business could he have\Nwith someone like that?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.36,0:14:20.37,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that you, Kisuke Urahara?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.06,0:14:23.45,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What brings you to\Na place like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.45,0:14:25.81,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I came because I needed to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.56,0:14:32.20,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Kurotsuchi Mayuri.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.12,0:14:38.32,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Won't you leave here with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.16,0:14:43.89,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Who…is this dude?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.76,0:14:45.76,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.76,0:14:48.51,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You called someone you met\Nfor the first time "dude."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.06,0:14:52.37,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Quite a disrespectful boy,\NI must say.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.37,0:14:53.34,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Boy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.63,0:14:54.93,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you calling a boy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.93,0:14:56.43,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.43,0:14:58.08,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You want me to\Nshow you my boobs?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.08,0:14:59.34,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Freak! You look like\Na weird boiled dumpling!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.34,0:15:01.85,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,– Please forgive her foul mouth.\N– See?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.85,0:15:03.24,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,She is my squad's…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.56,0:15:05.10,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on and take\Na good look at these!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.10,0:15:06.28,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Lieutenant.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.00,0:15:08.66,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,– Lieutenant…\N– You see that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.00,0:15:10.53,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,– You were promoted?\N– Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.53,0:15:11.56,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm telling you to look at these,\Nyou idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.56,0:15:12.99,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,– Congratulations.\N– Hello?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.21,0:15:14.33,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.00,0:15:18.43,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Getting back to the subject,\Ncan I have your answer?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.16,0:15:23.66,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean to your hare-brained idea\Nof leaving here with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.66,0:15:24.40,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.70,0:15:25.92,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,No thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.46,0:15:28.48,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay then! Let's go back!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.48,0:15:30.02,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,If this dude doesn't want to leave,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.02,0:15:32.38,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,we'd just be wasting our time\Nby staying here, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.24,0:15:36.11,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.36,0:15:39.55,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I am satisfied with my life here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.91,0:15:41.59,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I have no need to leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.03,0:15:45.33,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That couldn't possibly be true.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.33,0:15:48.03,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Not in this place where\Nthere's nothing to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.03,0:15:49.69,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Then let me ask you…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.69,0:15:53.00,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you want to\Nget me out of here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.00,0:15:55.30,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I need your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.59,0:15:58.18,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's dispense with\Nthe frivolous lies.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.18,0:16:00.50,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I could see through\Nthat one like an X-ray.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.84,0:16:02.31,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You got me there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.31,0:16:04.98,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I am making you\Noverly cautious, aren't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.98,0:16:07.00,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I cannot figure you out.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.40,0:16:09.48,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You are an unpleasant fellow.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.93,0:16:15.55,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe in your skills.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.13,0:16:17.61,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That is the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.06,0:16:22.83,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I am considering creating\Nan organization
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.83,0:16:24.46,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,under the control of Squad 12
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.46,0:16:27.53,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,unlike anything ever seen\Nin the Soul Society.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.20,0:16:30.44,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm calling it the "Department\Nof Research and Development."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.96,0:16:34.71,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to assume the seat\Nof deputy department head.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.96,0:16:35.91,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.49,0:16:40.24,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You want me to work under you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.24,0:16:43.64,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That's correct.\NIt's not a bad offer, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.99,0:16:46.35,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You'd be second\Nin command to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.35,0:16:47.22,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.15,0:16:52.19,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,If I die, you would\Nhave total control.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.12,0:17:05.30,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You certainly are\Nan unpleasant fellow.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.73,0:17:23.14,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, impressive,\Nvery impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.14,0:17:26.06,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Practicing hard, I see,\NByakuya.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.56,0:17:35.03,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandfather!\NYou have returned to the mansion.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.03,0:17:38.00,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you come to rest here today\Nrather than at the barracks?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.00,0:17:39.00,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.00,0:17:40.47,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad you did.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.16,0:17:43.58,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a long time since\NI've been able to talk with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.58,0:17:45.68,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It makes me very happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.13,0:17:47.16,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.16,0:17:49.17,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what do you say, Byakuya?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.17,0:17:51.65,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you call it a day\Nfor practice today.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.96,0:17:54.02,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I brought someone\Nhere to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.02,0:17:54.72,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Here to see me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.39,0:17:58.61,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You've appeared, cat monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.93,0:18:01.93,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,"Cat Monster"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.93,0:18:03.80,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that what I get for coming\Nto see you, Byakuya-boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.80,0:18:06.26,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,And to think I came\Nall this way to visit!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.50,0:18:10.34,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Quiet! When did I ever say\NI wanted you to come and visit me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.73,0:18:13.10,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,As the next head\Nof the Kuchiki Clan,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.10,0:18:14.47,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need fun and games!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.47,0:18:15.44,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.40,0:18:20.31,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.53,0:18:23.73,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It may be just fun and games,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.73,0:18:26.73,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,but I worry about the future of\Nthe Kuchiki Clan if its next head
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.73,0:18:29.20,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,of the House has his topknot tie\Neasily taken away by a girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.20,0:18:32.25,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay right where you are,\NYoruichi Shihoin.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.25,0:18:33.99,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,With my Flash Step, I'll…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.99,0:18:36.46,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Byakuya Kuchiki!\NI have beaten you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.23,0:18:41.53,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.03,0:18:44.93,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Seems you really\Nwant to make me angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.60,0:18:46.73,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.00,0:18:49.41,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Then you'll find out for yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.51,0:18:54.78,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That my Flash Step\Nhas far surpassed yours!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.39,0:18:57.19,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh good grief…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.19,0:19:00.02,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Byakuya would reach\Na whole new level
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.02,0:19:02.85,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,if he could only get rid\Nof his quick temper.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.96,0:19:09.29,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then, maybe\NI'll have some tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.92,0:19:13.96,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.86,0:19:26.16,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That smile of yours is\Nas powerful as always.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.16,0:19:27.20,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.50,0:19:28.33,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,So about the…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.33,0:19:32.42,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll say it again,\NI won't be your lieutenant.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.92,0:19:36.89,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say it again.\NYou'll hurt my feelings even more.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.45,0:19:42.36,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,There are lots of others who deserve\Nto become captain-level before me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.10,0:19:44.41,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you saying that\Nout of obligation?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.41,0:19:47.06,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that's so you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.90,0:19:52.52,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, have you heard?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.52,0:19:53.95,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,About what?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.95,0:19:56.61,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm told there's a prodigy,\Nthe first one since you,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.61,0:19:58.05,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,among this year's recruits.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.05,0:20:00.31,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm no prodigy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.73,0:20:02.03,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,This child…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.70,0:20:06.28,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,He graduated from Soul Reaper\NAcademy in just one year.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.73,0:20:08.75,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,One year?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.23,0:20:10.66,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That's impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.66,0:20:11.96,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you agree?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.30,0:20:13.61,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I think…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.10,0:20:18.40,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Kuchiki's grandson\NByakuya is about that age.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.40,0:20:20.71,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that cocky one.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.71,0:20:22.19,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, that one.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.19,0:20:25.20,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I think the kid's about the\N same age or slightly younger.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.96,0:20:27.18,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I hear a Seat Officer's position
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.18,0:20:29.41,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,will be readied for him when he enters the squad.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.41,0:20:30.70,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.70,0:20:33.89,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like we've got ourselves\Nsomeone with quite a future.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.89,0:20:36.74,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That'll make my chances\Nfor a lieutenant position
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.74,0:20:38.21,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,even more distant.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.21,0:20:39.68,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't sound so happy about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.25,0:20:42.16,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,So, who is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.16,0:20:44.15,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Who gets that new recruit?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.53,0:20:47.36,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Well…I believe…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.76,0:20:49.35,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,He'll be joining Squad 5.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.86,0:20:53.92,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.83,0:20:56.80,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Your skill is even better\Nthan I had heard.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.88,0:21:00.00,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me your name again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.70,0:21:01.47,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Gin…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.26,0:21:04.94,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Gin Ichimaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.23,0:21:07.82,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,How was our Third Seat?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.82,0:21:10.91,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Awful. No competition at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.03,0:21:13.62,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.73,0:21:16.31,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Glad to hear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.36,0:21:24.85,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,After swinging toward the past\Nand giving a flash glimpse in time,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.85,0:21:28.25,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,several more years pass as we move
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.36,0:21:32.98,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,toward the crux of the incident.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.02,0:21:39.83,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,ONE HUNDRED ONE YEARS AGO
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.03,0:23:23.01,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to be my lieutenant.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.01,0:23:26.50,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What it means is that if I die,\Nyou will have complete control.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.50,0:23:28.19,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this about, out of the blue?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.19,0:23:31.29,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to imitate Kisuke Urahara.\NHow'd I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.23,0:23:34.99,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not even funny.\NPlease stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.99,0:23:37.11,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Substitute Soul Reaper\NWork Journal!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.82,0:23:40.46,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,INTERACTING WITH REGIONAL HEADS
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.11,0:23:38.96,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Interacting with Soul Reapers\N	who are the regional heads
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.96,0:23:41.00,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,is also an important duty of\Nthe Substitute Soul Reaper.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.65,0:23:44.56,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard!\NYou're taking my work again!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.56,0:23:46.93,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh…umm…you are…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.93,0:23:48.44,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you forget, Ichigo?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.44,0:23:51.01,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,He was put in charge of\NKarakura Town after me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.93,0:23:54.34,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,SOUL REAPER IN CHARGE\NOF KARAKURA TOWN
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.01,0:23:54.34,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Kurumada…do…de…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.68,0:23:55.57,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Sir Kurumatta.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.57,0:23:56.81,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Now you, too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.81,0:23:58.33,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Then we'll call him Kurumaebi!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.33,0:24:00.00,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean,\N"then we'll call him"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.00,0:24:02.32,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,– This is too much trouble.\N– Kuruma…Kuruma…Kuruma…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.32,0:24:03.69,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll just leave it at Kuruma!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.32,0:24:05.02,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,INTERACTING WITH REGIONAL HEADS
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.69,0:24:05.69,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,